message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "DED Mémoriel Filter: Selective Inference Without Fine-Tuning"
authors:
  - family-names: Renno
    given-names: François
    affiliation: "Synoptisme Research Initiative"
    country: TH
repository-code: "https://github.com/HarmoIA/DED-memoriel"
